* {{Cite magazine |last=Keys |first=C.M.|date=January 1908|title=The Builders I: The House of Morgan |magazine={{link-en|The World's Work}}|volume=15|issue=2|pages=9779–9704|url= https://books.google.com/books?id=hKPvxXgBN1oC&pg=PA9779|access-date=July 10, 2009}}
* Moody, John. [https://archive.org/details/mastersofcapitaljohn00moodiala ''The Masters of Capital: A Chronicle of Wall Street''] (1921)
* Rottenberg, Dan. ''The Man Who Made Wall Street''. University of Pennsylvania Press.
{{Refend}}

